    {
        "content": "<p>Is there a way to get the output of pretty printed syntax as a string?</p>\n<p>For example:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Elab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Command</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">run_cmd</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mkIdent</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mkIdent</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`X</span><span class=\"o\">)})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">logInfo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stx</span>\n<span class=\"c1\">-- variable {a : X}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>How can I get the string <code>\"variable {a : X}\"</code> out of <code>stx</code>?</p>",
        "id": 450888483,
        "sender_full_name": "Damiano Testa",
        "timestamp": 1720766587
    },
    {
        "content": "<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Elab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Command</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PrettyPrinter</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Elab</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">Command</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">run_cmd</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">do</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">let</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stx</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">`</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"kn\">variable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mkIdent</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">mkIdent</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"ss\">`X</span><span class=\"o\">)})</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">logInfo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">liftTermElabM</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">$</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ppCommand</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stx</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>For other syntax categories, see <code>ppCategory</code> etc.</p>",
        "id": 450928446,
        "sender_full_name": "Jannis Limperg",
        "timestamp": 1720778878
    },
    {
